description:
Happy to be surrounded again by my fans lol.

And Im thrilled to announce that copies of Filipino Vegan have been replenished and restocked on Amazon US!

Each book is signed and imported from the Philippines. 

To those patiently waiting, maraming salamat po. I hope you find the book valuable and helpful in cooking and gaining a new perspective. Im looking forward to hearing about your journey. Please feel free to let me know and message me how it goes.

For photos of the rest of the recipes, you can go to the website astigvegan.com/photos-from-the-cookbook-filipino-vegan instead of scanning each of the QR codes. 

Thanks again. Hopefully someday the book will extend not just outside of the motherland and into the US, but also in other parts of the world where it might help someone reconnect with their roots and culture while celebrating an all-vegan feast. Its possible, all it takes is a little imagination, creativity, and inspiration. May Filipino Vegan lead to you all three! I hope you enjoy and Kain na, lets eat!

#veganinthephilippines #veganfinds #astigvegan #filipinovegan #veganfilipino #vegan
